page.title: 01KINGMOOR SUMMARY
page.content: {KINGMOOR SUMMARY Kingmoor comprises Lowry Hill & Newfield Estates, Kingstown with its Industrial Estate, Moorville & Kingmoor Nature Reserve within Carlisle City Boundary & Cargo & Harker villages, Carlisle RAF Maintenance Unit (14MU) & Carlisle Marshalling Yard outwith. The M6 motorway & the A74 dual carriageway join at Junction 44, Greymoorhill Interchange, just north of the city. The main London_Glasgow railway line crosses SE_NW. The southern boundary of our survey area is the River Eden & Belah Estate.
